<Title>Cabin Air Compressor (CAC) Flow Sensors</Title>
<DispatchCondition repairInterval="C" nbrInstalled="2" nbrRequired="1" maintIndicator="(M)">
<DispatchConditionRemarks>
<Para>One may be inoperative provided one of the associated CACs is deactivated.</Para>
</DispatchConditionRemarks>
<Note>
<Para>The airplane must also be dispatched using MEL item 21-51-01.</Para>
</Note>
<DispatchProcedure>
<MaintenanceProcedure>
<Para>Deactivate one CAC associated with the inoperative sensor.  Use MEL item 21-51-01 (M) procedure.</Para>
</MaintenanceProcedure>
</DispatchProcedure>
